        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr>
          <td><strong>Credential Stuffing</strong><br/><small style="color:#777;">Automated replay of breached credentials at scale</small></td>
          <td><span class="severity-badge sev-critical">Critical</span></td>
          <td>Rate limiting (5 req/15 min per IP), account lockout, TOTP second factor required for MFA accounts</td>
          <td>
            <span class="tc-ref">LOGIN-07</span>
            <span class="tc-ref">LOGIN-02</span>
          </td>
          <td><span class="status-badge status-PASS">PASS</span></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td><strong>Password Spraying</strong><br/><small style="color:#777;">Low-and-slow password guessing across many accounts</small></td>
          <td><span class="severity-badge sev-high">High</span></td>
          <td>Global rate limit by IP (Upstash Redis), lockout after 5 failures, generic error messages</td>
          <td>
            <span class="tc-ref">LOGIN-07</span>
            <span class="tc-ref">LOGIN-03</span>
            <span class="tc-ref">LOGIN-04</span>
          </td>
          <td><span class="status-badge status-PASS">PASS</span></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td><strong>Account Enumeration</strong><br/><small style="color:#777;">Differentiating valid vs invalid accounts via error timing/messages</small></td>
          <td><span class="severity-badge sev-high">High</span></td>
          <td>Identical error message for wrong password and non-existent user; constant-time comparison</td>
          <td>
            <span class="tc-ref">LOGIN-03</span>
            <span class="tc-ref">LOGIN-04</span>
          </td>
          <td><span class="status-badge status-PASS">PASS</span></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td><strong>Session Fixation / Hijacking</strong><br/><small style="color:#777;">Attacker pre-sets session token or intercepts cookie</small></td>
          <td><span class="severity-badge sev-high">High</span></td>
          <td>New session token issued on each login, HttpOnly + Secure + SameSite=Lax cookie flags</td>
          <td>
            <span class="tc-ref">LOGIN-09</span>
            <span class="tc-ref">LOGIN-01</span>
          </td>
          <td><span class="status-badge status-PASS">PASS</span></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td><strong>Cross-Site Scripting (XSS)</strong><br/><small style="color:#777;">Injecting script via form fields reflected in error messages</small></td>
          <td><span class="severity-badge sev-high">High</span></td>
          <td>React JSX auto-escaping, Content-Security-Policy header (script-src 'self')</td>
          <td>
            <span class="tc-ref">LOGIN-10</span>
          </td>
          <td><span class="status-badge status-PASS">PASS</span></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td><strong>MFA Bypass / Code Reuse</strong><br/><small style="color:#777;">Reusing an already-consumed TOTP code; step-skipping</small></td>
          <td><span class="severity-badge sev-high">High</span></td>
          <td>Server-side TOTP verification with 30 s window + drift ±1, one-time use enforced via nonce store</td>
          <td>
            <span class="tc-ref">LOGIN-08</span>
            <span class="tc-ref">LOGIN-02</span>
          </td>
          <td><span class="status-badge status-PASS">PASS</span></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td><strong>Phishing-Resistant Auth (FIDO2)</strong><br/><small style="color:#777;">Absence of hardware-bound authentication leaves phishing risk open</small></td>
          <td><span class="severity-badge sev-medium">Medium</span></td>
          <td>WebAuthn passkey support implemented; Playwright automation blocked on virtual authenticator config</td>
          <td>
            <span class="tc-ref">LOGIN-13</span>
            <span style="font-size:10px;color:#856404;">(BLOCKED)</span>
          </td>
          <td><span class="status-badge status-BLOCKED">PARTIAL</span></td>
